**/resource/

# --- Python Patterns ---
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.Python
env/
venv/
.venv/
pip-log.txt
pip-delete-this-directory.txt

# --- System Patterns ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

